data.description:
MAKE YOURSELF AT HOME in this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 1.5 story home in the heart of town. The front porch welcomes you! Love the gorgeous woodwork & built-ins in the spacious living room. Gather in the formal dining room & enjoy cooking in the updated kitchen. Main floor bedroom makes a great office! Enjoy
3 bedrooms upstairs with an updated ¾ bathroom. Plenty of storage in the unfinished lower level! Tons of potential with the 1 car garage.  A fully fenced in backyard is ready for games, pets, or gardens. Super location being close to schools, town & I94. NOW is the time to make this your HOME! Call for a tour today!
